title: 12/07 Fantasy Football Podcast: Start or Sit (AFC); Startometer!
description:
We begin with some Week 14 sleepers (1:50) like Frank Gore before breaking out the Startometer (4:00) for LeSean McCoy, Giovani Bernard, a number of DSTs and more ... All the news & notes you can handle including a Mark Ingram update (14:50), WRs who could actually impact the TE rankings if they play (16:50), defensive injuries and more ... NYJ-DEN (20:28), GB-CLE (28:24), OAK-KC (37:20), SEA-JAC (44:00), SF-HOU (48:24), WAS-LAC (53:51), IND-BUF (57:05), CHI-CIN (1:00:00) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
